# 👨‍💻 Ahmad Sanoh | Portfolio

![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.0-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green)
![Tailwind](https://img.shields.io/badge/CSS-Tailwind-38B2AC?logo=tailwind-css)

A premium, responsive portfolio website designed to showcase my journey as a Web & Mobile Developer and Data Scientist. Inspired by the "Trueman" aesthetic, this site features a minimalist split-layout design with a seamless user experience.

🔗 Live Demo: [https://ahmadsanoh.github.io/My-Portfolio/](https://ahmadsanoh.github.io/My-Portfolio/)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

## ✨ Features

* 🌓 Dual Theme Engine: Smooth transition between Dark and Light modes with persistent local storage.
* 🌍 Multilingual Support: Integrated Google Translate API for French and English accessibility.
* 📱 Fully Responsive: Optimized for all devices, from mobile screens to ultra-wide monitors.
* 🚀 Interactive UI:

  * Dynamic typing effects using Typed.js.
  * Scroll-triggered animations powered by AOS.
  * Sticky sidebar navigation for quick access to contact info and social links.
* 🎨 Modern Tech Stack: Built with utility-first CSS for high performance and easy maintenance.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* Framework: [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/)
* Icons: [Font Awesome 6](https://fontawesome.com/)
* Animations: [AOS (Animate On Scroll)](https://michalsnik.github.io/aos/) & [Typed.js](https://mattboldt.com/demos/typed-js/)
* Language: HTML5, Modern JavaScript

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

